metadata.name: The Man of the Alley
metadata.description:
In the early morning hours of Christmas Day 2021, a blizzard hit the City of Vancouver, Canada. 

The snow was falling seamlessly, the streets were sparsely populated while the residents in their adorned homes were getting ready for gatherings and celebrations.

Under such harsh weather conditions, the Man of the Alley suddenly emerged from the back door of his shop as he was meticulously preparing for opening up and serving the patrons.
